_010_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11380,"position":5,"arabic":"١٠","translation":"(১০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":11,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعْمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثْ","translation":"and of thy Sustainer's blessings shalt thou [ever] speak.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6090.mp3","surahId":93,"words":[{"id":12598,"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا","translation":"আর প্রসঙ্গ","audioUrl":"wbw/093_011_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12599,"position":2,"arabic":"بِنِعْمَةِ","translation":"অনুগ্রহের","audioUrl":"wbw/093_011_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12600,"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","translation":"তোমার রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/093_011_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12601,"position":4,"arabic":"فَحَدِّثْ","translation":"অতঃপর বর্ণনা করো","audioUrl":"wbw/093_011_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12602,"position":5,"arabic":"١١","translation":"(১১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]}]}